00:00:08.641 --> 00:00:11.044
So my name is Nathaniel Steeves,
and I'm a vice principal

00:00:11.044 --> 00:00:13.079
at Birchmount School
and at Birchmount School.

00:00:13.079 --> 00:00:13.947
We have a lot of fun

00:00:13.947 --> 00:00:17.617
and engaging activities for our students,
but also for our community members.

00:00:18.284 --> 00:00:20.620
One of those being the fall fair.

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:23.456
And this happens
once a year, in the fall.

00:00:23.456 --> 00:00:26.559
And it's a great way for staff
to meet parents and guardians,

00:00:26.559 --> 00:00:27.927
but it's also a great way for the

00:00:27.927 --> 00:00:31.464
the guardians and, and parents to meet us
and put a face to our names.

00:00:31.765 --> 00:00:35.735
It also allows the students
a little bit of of activity time,

00:00:35.902 --> 00:00:39.005
where they also are engaging with staff
members who they might not be aware of.

00:00:39.005 --> 00:00:42.008
And this is done through a scavenger hunt
that we put together.

00:00:42.208 --> 00:00:46.079
And in that scavenger hunt, the students
and their parents or guardians

00:00:46.079 --> 00:00:48.348
are going to different people
meeting the tech teacher,

00:00:48.348 --> 00:00:51.351
meeting their face and teacher
based on the clues that they are given.

00:00:52.218 --> 00:00:54.354
The Fall fair also includes games

00:00:54.354 --> 00:00:57.924
and some prizes that the students
and parents can win through those games.

00:00:57.924 --> 00:01:00.794
And we also include
culturally inclusive food.

00:01:00.794 --> 00:01:04.964
So we make sure that dietary restrictions
are are taken account for.

00:01:05.965 --> 00:01:06.533
The Fall Fair

00:01:06.533 --> 00:01:09.636
came to be a few years ago
as a way to engage

00:01:09.636 --> 00:01:13.039
the community and and bridge
the gap between home and school.

00:01:13.073 --> 00:01:14.874
It's a great way as a new person,

00:01:14.874 --> 00:01:17.877
as a new member of the school community,
to meet members of the school.

00:01:17.877 --> 00:01:19.079
It creates that rapport.

00:01:19.079 --> 00:01:20.513
So when you are calling home

00:01:20.513 --> 00:01:24.084
or when you are in meetings with parents,
you've already met most of them.

00:01:24.484 --> 00:01:27.487
And it allows for easier communication.

00:01:27.954 --> 00:01:30.957
At virtual school, we also have

00:01:31.057 --> 00:01:33.993
movie nights and the movie nights.

