We allow, parents and their children

00:01:43.770 --> 00:01:46.873
to bring pillows, blankets, cozy chairs.

00:01:47.173 --> 00:01:49.876
This creates
a great environment for that.

00:01:49.876 --> 00:01:52.112
It's also a cheaper option
than going to the movies.

00:01:53.179 --> 00:01:54.481
This

00:01:54.481 --> 00:01:57.484
